President Muhammadu Buhari clocks 77 years today and his wife, Aisha Buhari, has lavished her husband with sweet words. The First Lady, who described her husband as ‘incorruptible,’ prayed for God’s protection, guidance and good health to enable him to continue steering the affairs of the nation. Taking to her Twitter, Aisha shared lovely photos of Nigeria’s first family, as they all gathered to cut his birthday cake. She wrote: Happy Birthday to MY incorruptible GMB. I wish you Allah’s Guidance Protection and Good Health to continue steering the affairs of our dear nation. Long Live GMB Long Live Federal Republic of Nigeria. <img class="size-full wp-image-1371383 aligncenter" src="https://i1.wp.com/www.bellanaija.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191217_091846.jpg?resize=680%2C453&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="680" height="453" data-recalc-dims="1" />  Photo Credit: @aishambuhari The post “Happy birthday my incorruptible GMB” – Aisha Buhari Pens Heartfelt Message to Celebrate President Buhari’s Birthday appeared first on BellaNaija – Showcasing Africa to the world. Read today!. Source: Bella Naija Nigeria’s First Lady, Aisha Buhari took to social media to celebrate her husband President Buhari who turned 77 today December 17. The First Lady described President Buhari as ‘incorruptible’ as she prayed for God’s protection, guidance and good health to continue steering the affairs of the nation. Aisha Buhari who… December 17, 2019 In "Entertainment" First Lady Aisha Buhari on Tuesday joined millions of Nigerians to celebrate Nigerian President Muhammadu Buhari as he clocked 77. Aisha Buhari in a simple message on her verified Twitter account wished her husband, Allah’s guidance and good health. The Twitter post was accompanied by pictures of the First Lady… December 17, 2019 In "News" Abuja – The wife of the President, Mrs Aisha Buhari, has commiserated with the first lady of Sierra Leone, Mrs Sia Koroma over the unfortunate mudslide that killed over 300 people in Sier